{"tid":1381352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最成功一役","createTime":"2019-07-29T08:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T11:51:02.000Z","uid":89538,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0739b18aa6f3e4475f62d90c05d46814b0d2afe8","tid":1381352,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:18:20.000Z","msg":"大家記唔記得最成功係邊一次？<br />\n唔係沙田唔係立會<br />\n係警總呀！<br />\n<br />\n唔只係成功在用雞蛋<br />\n最成功係無乜人受傷 大家走得甩<br />\n記唔記得d狗一大堆係灣仔同其他區上哂gear想包圍<br />\n但我地be water走左佢地得個吉？<br />\n仲要慢慢洗番乾淨面牆<br />\n<br />\n唔好再晚晚都佔路勇武啦 一時勇一時休息 我地從來都知路會一時三刻就搞掂<br />\n長期戰就要保留實力 線上線下 文宣起底組和理非勇武一齊努力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024f9493ad792e238ec953272082997659da95b2","tid":1381352,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:51:02.000Z","msg":"雞蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多人一開始唔睇好"}]}